             was indicted for <rs id="t17800628-110-off549" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17800628-110-off549" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17800628-110-off549" type="offenceSubcategory" value="riot"></interp>
               that he, together with an hundred other persons and more, did, unlawfully, riotously, and tomultuously, assemble, on the <rs id="t17800628-110-cd550" type="crimeDate">5th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800628-110-off549 t17800628-110-cd550"></join>, to the disturbance of the publick peace, and did begin to demolish and pull down the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17800628-110-victim1438" type="victimName">
                           Mary 
                           Crook
                        <interp inst="t17800628-110-victim1438" type="surname" value="Crook"></interp>
