                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>When was your house destroyed? - I went out on Sunday; it was destroyed on the Monday. It is the first house out of <placeName id="t17800628-110-crimeloc552">Little Moorfields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17800628-110-crimeloc552" type="placeName" value="Little Moorfields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17800628-110-crimeloc552" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800628-110-off549 t17800628-110-crimeloc552"></join>.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was not there on the Monday night; I never was before a justice in my life.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner called 
               <persName id="t17800628-110-person1442">
